summary: This is a simple fix for those who get the dreaded CTD during the Wolf Queen Quest.
descriptionHtml:
This is a simple fix for those who get the dreaded CTD during the Wolf Queen Quest. It is caused by changes to the Jarl outfit she is wearing by other mods. Instead of removing the offending mod(s) I chose to remove the outfit from Potema instead.

Simply drop this esp into the Skyrim Data Folder, make sure it\'s activated before your next playtime and poof ... No CTD
author: Cedrick Hammerfist
